WHITEPAPER — Narrative Tensor Architecture (NTA) for Multi-Frame Coherent Image Generation

A Hybrid Research + Product Executive Brief

───────────────────────────────────────────────

Page 1 — Executive Summary & System Architecture

⸻

Executive Summary

Modern generative image models—including Gemini Imagine—excel at producing high-fidelity single images but lack narrative continuity across frame sequences. Users requesting multi-frame stories (e.g., comics, animations, scene progression) frequently experience:
	•	Identity drift (faces, clothing, anatomy inconsistent)
	•	World drift (lighting/style resets between frames)
	•	Symbol disappearance (motifs inconsistently represented)
	•	Temporal incoherence (scenes ignore earlier events)

These limitations stem from a structural gap: the image model operates statelessly, treating each prompt as independent.

This whitepaper proposes the Narrative Tensor Architecture (NTA):
a lightweight, modular, inference-layer enhancement that introduces:
	•	Narrative State (NS) — persistent story memory
	•	Narrative Tensor Engine (NTE) — structured conditioning tensor
	•	Coherence Daemon Layer — identity, logic, and world consistency enforcers
	•	EchoFrame — state updating mechanism

The approach does not require retraining the core Gemini image model.
It augments the orchestration layer, enabling cinematic-grade narrative coherence.

⸻

System Architecture Overview

┌───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐
│                               USER PROMPT                                  │
└───────────────┬───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘
                │
                ▼
     ┌──────────────────┐
     │ Narrative State  │  (NS: characters, world, rules, history)
     │     Manager      │
     └───────┬──────────┘
             │  (NS injected into fusion process)
             ▼
     ┌──────────────────┐
     │ Narrative Tensor │  (NTE: fθ(prompt, NS) → NT)
     │     Engine       │
     └───────┬──────────┘
             │  (NT conditions model)
             ▼
┌───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐
│                       COHERENCE DAEMON LAYER                             │
│                                                                           │
│   ┌──────────┐   ┌──────────┐   ┌────────────┐   ┌─────────────┐         │
│   │ Ganglion │→→│  Spider   │→→│ Dragonfly φ │→→│ Mirror/Chk   │         │
│   │ (triage) │   │(relations)│  │ (persp.)   │   │ (audit)     │         │
│   └──────────┘   └──────────┘   └────────────┘   └─────────────┘         │
└───────────────┬──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘
                │
                ▼
      ┌───────────────────────┐
      │   Render Spec (R_s)   │  (clean, coherent conditioning packet)
      └──────────┬────────────┘
                 │
                 ▼
        ┌──────────────────┐
        │ Gemini Image     │
        │  Generator       │
        └──────────┬───────┘
                   │
                   ▼
         ┌─────────────────┐
         │    Output       │
         │    Image        │
         └────────┬────────┘
                  │
                  ▼
       ┌──────────────────────┐
       │   EchoFrame Update   │
       │ (state distillation) │
       └──────────┬───────────┘
                  │
                  ▼
   ┌──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐
   │     Updated Narrative State (NS') → supports next generation     │
   └──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘


